---
layout: layouts/base.njk
lang: fr
title: "Galerie Photos — Pomsky, Pomeranian & Husky — Élevage des Cimes Blanches"
description: "30 photos de nos chiots et chiens Pomsky, Pomeranian et Husky sibérien. La vie à l'Élevage des Cimes Blanches à Sierre, Valais."
permalink: "/galerie.html"
hreflang_fr: "/galerie.html"
hreflang_en: "/en/gallery.html"
---
<style>
.gallery-filters{display:flex;gap:.8rem;margin-bottom:2.5rem;flex-wrap:wrap}
.filter-btn{padding:.5rem 1.2rem;font-family:var(--sans);font-size:.72rem;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;border:1px solid var(--gris-clair);border-radius:20px;background:transparent;color:var(--gris);cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s}
.filter-btn.active,.filter-btn:hover{border-color:var(--or);color:var(--or)}
.gallery-grid{columns:4;column-gap:10px}
@media(max-width:900px){.gallery-grid{columns:3}}
@media(max-width:600px){.gallery-grid{columns:2}}
</style>

<div class="page-hero">
  <p class="page-hero__label">Galerie</p>
  <h1 class="page-hero__title">30 regards,<br><em style="font-style:italic;color:var(--or)">30 histoires</em></h1>
  <p class="page-hero__desc">Des nouveau-nés aux adultes, des premières neiges aux adoptions — la vie aux Cimes Blanches en images.</p>
</div>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="gallery-filters reveal">
      <button class="filter-btn active" data-filter="all">Tout</button>
      <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="chiots">🐾 Chiots</button>
      <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="pomsky">Pomsky</button>
      <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="pomeranian">Pomeranian</button>
      <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="husky">Husky</button>
      <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="famille">Familles</button>
      <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="nature">Nature & Alpes</button>
    </div>
    <div class="gallery-grid reveal">
      {% for photo in collections.galerie %}
      <div class="gallery-item" data-cat="{{ photo.data.categorie }}">
        <img src="{{ photo.data.image }}" alt="{{ photo.data.legende_fr }}">
        <div class="gallery-item__caption">{{ photo.data.legende_fr }}</div>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
document.querySelectorAll('.filter-btn').forEach(btn => {
  btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
    document.querySelectorAll('.filter-btn').forEach(b => b.classList.remove('active'));
    btn.classList.add('active');
    const f = btn.dataset.filter;
    document.querySelectorAll('.gallery-item').forEach(item => {
      item.style.display = (f === 'all' || item.dataset.cat.includes(f)) ? '' : 'none';
    });
  });
});
</script>
